}, {"text": "2,884.4", "bbox": [607.4, 694.0, 668.4, 714.8]}, {"text": "2,896.2", "bbox": [701.1, 694.0, 762.2, 714.8]}, {"text": "2,881.9", "bbox": [789.0, 694.0, 850.0, 714.8]}, {"text": "1,770", "bbox": [896.8, 694.0, 943.8, 714.8]}, {"text": "1,583", "bbox": [990.6, 694.0, 1037.5, 714.8]}, {"text": "1,404", "bbox": [1090.2, 694.0, 1137.1, 714.8]}, {"text": "Intermodal", "bbox": [105.0, 737.2, 192.1, 757.9]}, {"text": "1,971", "bbox": [340.3, 737.2, 387.2, 757.9]}, {"text": "1,826", "bbox": [434.0, 737.2, 480.9, 757.9]}, {"text": "1,537", "bbox": [527.7, 737.2, 574.7, 757.9]}, {"text": "3,256.5", "bbox": [607.4, 737.2, 668.4, 757.9]}, {"text": "3,154.9", "bbox": [701.1, 737.2, 762.2, 757.9]}, {"text": "2,891.5", "bbox": [789.0, 737.2, 850.1, 757.9]}, {"text": "605", "bbox": [911.0, 737.2, 943.8, 757.9]}, {"text": "579", "bbox": [1004.7, 737.2, 1037.6, 757.9]}, {"text": "531", "bbox": [1104.4, 737.2, 1137.2, 757.9]}, {"text": "Total", "bbox": [105.0, 780.3, 168.1, 801.0]}, {"text": "$ 9,407", "bbox": [311.2, 780.3, 387.2, 801.0]}, {"text": "$ 8,527", "bbox": [405.0, 780.3, 480.9, 801.0]}, {"text": "$ 7,312", "bbox": [498.8, 780.3, 574.7, 801.0]}, {"text": "7,900.9", "bbox": [607.4, 780.3, 668.4, 801.0]}, {"text": "7,786.5", "bbox": [701.1, 780.3, 762.2, 801.0]}, {"text": "7,464.2", "bbox": [789.0, 780.3, 850.1, 801.0]}, {"text": "$", "bbox": [867.9, 780.3, 877.2, 801.0]}, {"text": "1,191", "bbox": [896.9, 780.3, 943.8, 801.0]}, {"text": "$ 1,095", "bbox": [961.6, 780.3, 1037.5, 801.0]}, {"text": "$", "bbox": [1055.3, 780.3, 1064.7, 801.0]}, {"text": "980", "bbox": [1104.3, 780.3, 1137.2, 801.0]}, {"text": "Revenues increased $880 million, or 10%, in 2006 and $1.2 billion, or 17%, in 2005.  As shown in the following", "bbox": [112.5, 828.7, 1152.0, 854.1]}, {"text": "table, both revenue improvements were the result of increased average revenues per unit, including fuel", "bbox": [112.5, 855.1, 1067.7, 880.4]}, {"text": "surcharges, and, to a lesser extent in 2006 than for 2005, higher traffic volumes.", "bbox": [112.5, 881.4, 862.2, 906.7]}, {"text": "Revenue Variance Analysis", "bbox": [327.0, 934.2, 600.0, 959.6]}, {"text": "Increases", "bbox": [418.0, 960.5, 508.8, 985.8]}, {"text": "2006 vs. 2005", "bbox": [496.9, 1013.2, 631.8, 1038.6]}, {"text": "2005 vs. 2004", "bbox": [668.8, 1013.2, 803.7, 1038.6]}, {"text": "($ in millions)", "bbox": [583.1, 1039.6, 718.7, 1064.9]}, {"text": "Revenue per unit/mix", "bbox": [112.5, 1092.2, 316.9, 1117.6]}, {"text": "$", "bbox": [493.1, 1092.2, 510.3, 1117.6]}, {"text": "755", "bbox": [601.3, 1092.2, 635.7, 1117.6]}, {"text": "$", "bbox": [661.8, 1092.2, 673.2, 1117.6]}, {"text": "899", "bbox": [774.4, 1092.2, 808.8, 1117.6]}, {"text": "Traffic volume (units)", "bbox": [112.5, 1118.6, 322.0, 1143.9]}, {"text": "125", "bbox": [601.3, 1118.6, 635.7, 1143.9]}, {"text": "316", "bbox": [774.4, 1118.6, 808.7, 1143.9]}, {"text": "Total", "bbox": [112.5, 1145.9, 195.4, 1171.2]}, {"text": "$", "bbox": [492.9, 1145.9, 510.1, 1171.2]}, {"text": "880", "bbox": [601.1, 1145.9, 635.5, 1171.2]}, {"text": "$", "bbox": [661.6, 1145.9, 673.0, 1171.2]}, {"text": "1,215", "bbox": [757.1, 1145.9, 808.7, 1171.2]}, {"text": "Both comparisons reflect large increases in average revenue per unit, a result of higher rates and increased fuel", "bbox": [112.5, 1201.7, 1134.0, 1227.1]}, {"text": "surcharges.  All market groups collected significant fuel surcharges, which accounted for approximately 40% of", "bbox": [112.5, 1228.1, 1145.2, 1253.4]}, {"text": "the 2006 increase in revenues and about one-third of the 2005 increase.  At year-end 2006, fuel surcharge", "bbox": [112.5, 1254.5, 1085.0, 1279.8]}, {"text": "provisions covered approximately 91% of total revenues compared with about 85% at the end of 2005.  Traffic", "bbox": [112.5, 1280.9, 1135.0, 1306.2]}, {"text": "volume increased 1% in 2006, principally due to higher intermodal and metals/construction shipments.  In", "bbox": [112.5, 1307.2, 1091.9, 1332.6]}, {"text": "2005, traffic volume rose 4%, reflecting a 9% increase in intermodal shipments.  The favorable revenue per", "bbox": [112.5, 1333.6, 1104.0, 1358.9]}, {"text": "unit/mix variance in 2005 included an unfavorable mix component reflecting the 9% rise in intermodal traffic,", "bbox": [112.5, 1359.9, 1129.0, 1385.2]}, {"text": "which has a lower average revenue per unit.", "bbox": [112.5, 1386.2, 521.8, 1411.6]}, {"text": "On April 24, 2006, NS announced that it was revising its fuel surcharge program for non-intermodal traffic", "bbox": [112.5, 1439.0, 1099.4, 1464.3]}, {"text": "originating and moving on NS-issued tariffs and public quotes issued on or after July 1, 2006.  While the", "bbox": [112.5, 1465.4, 1079.5, 1490.7]}, {"text": "mechanics of the new fuel surcharge are generally the same as the previous fuel surcharge, the trigger price was", "bbox": [112.5, 1491.6, 1143.3, 1516.9]}]}